The father of a boy who was assaulted for undergoing a modern circumcision procedure is requesting well wishers for assistance with medical bills.Bedan Kinoti said he has been forced to spend Sh30,000 intended for the boy's form one fees on treatment after he was admitted in a private facility.The 15-year-old boy had been in seclusion following his circumcision when he was allegedly beaten by a group of boys for an entire night.He is currently undergoing treatment for a gash on his leg at Mitunguu Hospital in Imenti subcounty.He said he is unable to walk and has to rely on others to carry him so he can move around.Hospital nursing officer Livingston Mbogori said on Thursday that the boy requires corrective surgery to enable the wound to heal.The assault has been reported at Nkubu police station.